2. Requirements
In theory it should work on Pentium 133 and 16 RAM:) 
But only "default" mapset. New mapsets use exactly 133 MHZ and 16 MB.
It require SDL & SDL_image with libPNG support.
Optionally SDL_mixer & OpenGL.

3. Control
Game:
Left, Right - Move
Up, Down - Look up/down
Z - Jump
X - Run
Esc - Quit
Map editor:
Arrows - Move map
LMB - Place tile
MMB - Works like Q or W & X or like L
RMB - Probe tile
Shift + Arrows - Resize map
Ctrl + Arrows - Move map fastly
A, D or wheel - Select tile 
W, X - Select layer
Q - Change display mode
S - Save
L - List of all tiles
T (over text event) - Edit

4. Problems
a). If you have installed version 0.0.2, delete file $HOME/.oki

